---
title: Mediterranean Falafel Wrap with Chopped Salad, Garlicky Yogurt and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Saucy pita wraps are topped with wholesome hummus and golden falafel. The garlicky yoghurt is perfect alongside to dip your spiced sweet potato wedges into!
